I"Ÿ<h4 id="an-updated-space-time-cube-explorer-add-in-for-arcgis-pro-20-is-now-available">An updated Space Time Cube Explorer Add-in for ArcGIS Pro 2.0 is now available</h4>

<p>The Add-in can help you interact with and explore your space-time cube and analysis results created with the Space Time Pattern Mining toolbox in a simple and intuitive way.  This update includes many new features and enhancements such as the ability to output 3D polygons from a defined locations cube and enhanced time and range slider settings.</p>

<p>You can download the Add-in at <a href="http://www.esriurl.com/SpaceTimeCubeExplorer">http://www.esriurl.com/SpaceTimeCubeExplorer</a>.</p>
